==Upon entering Tarn's room==
* {{qact|Camera pans from the player to Tarn.}}
* '''Tarn:''' Who? How did you get here? Never mind. I'll deal with you myself!
* {{qact|Tarn casts a spell on the terror dog statues, bringing them to life. Tarn then turns into a mutant before sending his dogs after the player.}}

==Upon defeating mutant Tarn==
* '''Mutant tarn:''' {{overhead|Ha! I can't be slain that easily, fool!}}
* {{qact|Tarn transforms into a ghost.}}

==Upon killing ghost Tarn==
* {{mes|Killing Tarn Razorlor has greatly improved your Slayer knowledge. You gain 5000 Slayer XP.}}

==Taking Tarn's diary==
* {{qact|The camera pans to show the terror dog cages being unlocked.}}
* {{qact|Congratulations! Miniquest complete!}}
